      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That makes sense. I think the issue might be that I'm using a while loop with a manual counter. Here is a snippet of what I have:\n\n```python\ni = 0\nwhile i <= len(user_emails):\n    print(user_emails[i])\n    i += 1\n```\n\nDoes this look right to you? Why exactly does it crash?",
      "source": "evaluator",
